    {
        "content": "<p>This isn't always true, as <code>0 - 1 + 1 = 0 + 1 = 1 ≠ 0</code>, but see <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Nat.sub_add_cancel#doc\">docs#Nat.sub_add_cancel</a></p>",
